name: Leather Blouson
description: This sleek Leather Blouson distinguishes an ensemble with its brilliant green, inspired by the luminescent tones of the aurora borealis. The minimalist cut sets off tonal embossed House signatures on the back and chest. This sophisticated piece is easy to pair with both casual and tailored looks.

description: These casual washed denim shorts are perfect for summery days on the beach. Inspired by this collection’s nautical theme, they are embellished with a bleached-effect Monogram Fishnet print incorporating Monogram Flower details. The irregular motif, recalling watery distortions, lends a cool graphic vibe. This piece has a matching short-sleeved shirt for a fresh set.

name: Embroidered Denim Blouson
description: This sophisticated denim blouson is inspired by the fluctuating colours of the aurora borealis of this collection. Its graduated tie dye treatment, shifting from black to red, renders each piece unique. An embroidered gradient Monogram adds distinction, beginning at the shoulders and dispersing towards the waist. Perfect for the festive season, this clothing piece has matching trousers for a standout day-to-evening look.

name: Mix Leather Varsity Blouson
description: American tradition meets Louis Vuitton savoir-faire in this vibrant red varsity blouson inspired by Pharrell Williams’ past as a member of the drumline at Princess Anne High School in Virginia. This iconic piece from the Spring-Summer 2024 Show features an embossed tonal Damier on the white calfskin sleeves, a pearl-embroidered Louis Vuitton logo on the back and a crystal-embroidered PA patch on the chest that renders homage to Williams’ story.

name: Corteiz Club RTW Football Jersey 'Blue'
description: Inspired by the 1995 uniforms of Mexico City-based football Club América, the Corteiz Club RTW Football Jersey Blue is a retro-style football jersey from Corteiz released as part of the Spring/Summer 2023 (SS23) collection.Available in blue, this jersey is made of 100% cotton. It features the iconic Club América crest embroidered on the chest and the club’s navy blue, red, and yellow colors on the crest and diamond pattern on the front, arms, and back. Branding details include the Corteiz Allstarz logo at the midriff on the sponsor logo area, 'rulestheword' trademark branding embroidered in white on the right part of the chest, and an 'RTW 18' type on the back. Short sleeves and a V-neck design round out this jersey’s design.Our experts love this jersey’s design and color. The retro-style design in a blue colorway and contrasting tones on other details make this jersey a statement piece that can elevate any outfit. The Corteiz Club RTW Football Jersey Blue was released on June 16th, 2023, retailing at $128.

The elasticized waistband offers a secure fit.The Corteiz mula guerillaz cargos black green was released in March 2022 and retailed for $164.
